<plot>This made-for-video documentary treats classic movie fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of To Catch a Thief, Alfred Hitchcock's 1955 thriller about a retired catburglar who must track down a new thief before he takes the blame for the newcomer's crimes. Includes interviews with Hitchcock's daughter, Pamela, along with archive footage from the set of the film.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?353778</url></doc>
